'''天主教姆巴拉拉總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Mbararaensis}}；{{lang-en|Archdiocese of Mbarara}}）是[[烏干達|烏干達]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄四個教區。

==歷史==
'''魯文佐里宗座代牧區'''於1934年5月28日設立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=II |year=1935 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=269-270 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-27-1935-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425134719/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-27-1935-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-25 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1953年3月25日升為教區並易名為'''姆巴拉拉教區'''<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XX |year=1953 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=705-710 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-45-1953-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422193646/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-45-1953-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-22 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1999年1月2日升為總教區<ref>{{cite web |title=MBARARAËNSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19990102_diligentem-sane.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425133953/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19990102_diligentem-sane.html |archivedate=2020-04-25 |language=la |date=1999-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==現況==
總教區管轄[[西部區_(烏干達)|西部區]]東南部十一區，2004年時有901,384名教友（佔轄區總人口37.1%）、25個堂區和109位司鐸。

現任總主教為{{link-en|郎培·拜諾穆吉沙|Lambert Bainomugisha}}，榮休總主教為{{link-en|保祿·卡穆薩·巴基恩加|Paul Kamuza Bakyenga|保祿·K·巴基恩加}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 25.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/25/200425a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425113045/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/25/200425a.html |archivedate=2020-04-25 |language=en |date=2020-04-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

